<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-55-0793 </DOCNO><TEXT>The 'audatec' process control system for power plant automation is presentedas an example of how an information and control system may be designed.The automation system for the 100 MW power plants of East Germany ispresented. The central element of the 'audatec' process control systemis the information system at the power unit control level. Particularinterest is taken in solutions with high ease of operation and extensivecontrol structures which ensure optimisation and automatic operationalso during starting and shut off.</TEXT></DOC>